'''克里斯蒂安·罗杰里奥·贝尼特斯·贝坦柯特'''（'''{{lang|es|Christian Rogelio Benítez Betancourt}}'''，{{bd|1986年|5月1日|2013年|7月29日|catIdx=Benitez, Christian Rogelio}}），绰号'''Chucho'''，是一名已逝世的[[厄瓜多尔|厄瓜多尔]][[足球|足球]][[运动员|运动员]]，逝世时效力于[[卡塔尔星级足球联赛|卡塔尔星级足球联赛]]球队[[艾查殊体育俱乐部|阿尔贾什]]。他为[[厄瓜多尔国家足球队|厄瓜多尔国家足球队]]一共出场A级比赛58场，射进24球。

==个人生活==
贝尼特斯出生于[[厄瓜多尔|厄瓜多尔]]首都[[基多|基多]]，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ecuafutbol.org/Servicios/FichaJugadores.aspx?valor1=1715547665 |title=Ficha del jugador |trans_title=Player details |publisher=Ecuadorian Football Federation |language=es |accessdate=September 29, 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110819015157/http://www.ecuafutbol.org/Servicios/FichaJugadores.aspx?valor1=1715547665 |archivedate=2011-08-19 }}</ref>是足球运动员[[Ermen_Benítez|厄尔曼·贝尼特斯]]的儿子。<ref name=BBCBirmsign>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/8081077.stm |title=Birmingham sign striker Benitez |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=June 3, 2009 |accessdate=June 3, 2009 |archive-date=2009-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090608082712/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/8081077.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>2007年，他和前[[厄瓜多尔国家足球队|厄瓜多尔国家足球队]]成员[[Cléber_Chalá|克雷伯·查拉]]的女儿丽萨斯结婚。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.diario-extra.com/html/noticias.asp?codigo=20071224162232 |title=El mejor gol navideño |trans_title=The best goal for Christmas |newspaper=Diario Extra |language=es |date=December 24, 2007 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080524061540/http://www.diario-extra.com/html/noticias.asp?codigo=20071224162232 |archivedate=2008-05-24 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2013-07-30 }}</ref>2009年8月，丽萨斯为他生了一对[[双胞胎|双胞胎]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hoy.com.ec/noticias-ecuador/mellizos-mejores-goles-de-chucho-366572.html |title=Mellizos, mejores 'goles' de Chucho |trans_title=Twins, Chucho's best 'goals' |newspaper=Hoy |language=es |date=September 6, 2009 |accessdate=September 29, 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927101155/http://www.hoy.com.ec/noticias-ecuador/mellizos-mejores-goles-de-chucho-366572.html |archivedate=2011-09-27 }}</ref>

==俱乐部生涯==
===民族竞技===
2004年，贝尼特斯在厄瓜多尔球队[[民族竞技俱乐部_(厄瓜多尔)|民族竞技]]开始职业足球生涯。在民族竞技的三年半时间里，他在联赛出场83次，射进29球，获得2005赛季秋季和2006赛季[[厄瓜多尔足球甲级联赛|厄瓜多尔足球甲级联赛]]冠军。由于他的出色表现，也一度引起[[瓦伦西亚足球俱乐部|瓦伦西亚]]等西班牙球会的注意，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aboutaball.co.uk/footballnews/View.php?ArticleID=172 |title=Ecuador Team Guide |publisher=AboutABall |first=Walter |last=Townsend |date=June 26, 2007 |accessdate=September 25, 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090719161022/http://www.aboutaball.co.uk/footballnews/View.php?ArticleID=172 |archivedate=2009年7月19日 }}</ref>不过民族竞技对这些转会流言都予以否认。<ref>{{cite news |date=January 16, 2007 |url=http://www.cre.com.ec/Desktop.aspx?Id=283&e=91238 |title=El Nacional no conoce interès del Villareal |publisher=CRE Satelital Ecuador |language=es |accessdate=September 25, 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090405172140/http://www.cre.com.ec/Desktop.aspx?Id=283&e=91238 |archivedate=2009-04-05 }}</ref>

===桑托斯拉古纳===
2007年7月，贝尼特斯转会加盟[[墨西哥足球甲级联赛|墨西哥足球甲级联赛]]球队[[桑托斯拉古纳俱乐部|桑托斯拉古纳]]。贝尼特斯和[[Vicente_Matías_Vuoso|维森特·马蒂亚斯·武索]]的加盟增加球队的实力。2007年底，贝尼特斯获得厄瓜多尔海外最佳足球运动员的称号。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ecuafutbol.org/UI/detalle.aspx?seccion=1&categserie=7&nivel=0&subnivel=0&id=10893&tabla=N |title=Cristian Benítez premiado por AER como mejor Ecuatoriano en el exterior |publisher=Ecuador Football Federation |first=Joselo |last=Sánchez Pineda |date=December 13, 2007 |accessdate=September 25, 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071215215943/http://www.ecuafutbol.org/UI/detalle.aspx?seccion=1&categserie=7&nivel=0&subnivel=0&id=10893&tabla=N |archivedate=2007-12-15 }}</ref>虽然[[葡萄牙足球超级联赛|葡萄牙足球超级联赛]]豪门[[里斯本與本菲卡體育俱樂部|本菲卡]]对他表示强烈兴趣，<ref>{{cite news |date=November 25, 2007 |url=http://www.goal.com/es/Articolo.aspx?ContenutoId=492061 |title=Alexis Sánchez y Christian Benítez interesan al Benfica |publisher=Goal.com |language=es |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071126043429/http://www.goal.com/es/Articolo.aspx?ContenutoId=492061 |archivedate=2007-11-26 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2013-07-30 }}</ref>但他还是决定留在墨西哥，并帮助球队获得2008赛季秋季联赛冠军，个人也获得联赛最佳球员的称号。<ref name=FIFAMVP>{{cite web |url=http://www.fifa.com/worldfootball/clubfootball/news/newsid=835965.html |title=Santos reap golden harvest |publisher=FIFA |date=July 30, 2008 |accessdate=September 25, 2008 |archive-date=2014-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140917222615/http://www.fifa.com/worldfootball/clubfootball/news/newsid=835965.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===伯明翰城===
[[File:Chucho.jpg|200px]]。]]
2009年6月3日，[[英格兰足球超级联赛|英格兰足球超级联赛]]球队[[伯明翰城足球俱乐部|伯明翰城]]宣布贝尼特斯以创俱乐部纪录的身价加盟并和球队签约3年，媒体预测转会价格在600万英镑至900万英镑之间。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghampost.net/midlands-birmingham-sport/west-midlands-sports/birmingham-city-fc/2009/06/04/birmingham-city-pay-record-9m-for-ecuador-striker-christian-benitez-65233-23788306/ |title=Birmingham City pay record £9m for Ecuador striker Christian Benitez |work=Birmingham Post |first=Andy |last=Walker |date=June 4, 2009 |accessdate=June 14, 2009 |archive-date=2012-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120313144012/http://www.birminghampost.net/midlands-birmingham-sport/west-midlands-sports/birmingham-city-fc/2009/06/04/birmingham-city-pay-record-9m-for-ecuador-striker-christian-benitez-65233-23788306/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>不过这次转会成功与否受到球员是否能获得劳工证和是否通过体检的限制。<ref name=BBCBirmsign/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/page/News/NewsDetail/0,,10412~1685586,00.html |title=Blues make record signing |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=June 3, 2009 |accessdate=June 3, 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090606182725/http://www.bcfc.com/page/News/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10412~1685586%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-06-06 }}</ref>结果在体检中意外发现贝尼特斯有膝盖问题，<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.net/birmingham-sport/birmingham-city-fc/birmingham-city-fc-news/2009/07/06/medical-concerns-delay-benitez-s-9m-move-to-blues-97319-24084241/ |title=Medical concerns delay Benitez's £9m move to Blues |first=Colin |last=Tattum |date=July 6, 2009 |accessdate=July 7, 2009 |work=Birmingham Mail |archive-date=2012-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120328135743/http://www.birminghammail.net/birmingham-sport/birmingham-city-fc/birmingham-city-fc-news/2009/07/06/medical-concerns-delay-benitez-s-9m-move-to-blues-97319-24084241/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>导致两家-{}-俱乐部在保护伯明翰城利益的前提下重新进行转会谈判，最终达成转会协议为伯明翰先支付200万美元（120万英镑）作为初始费用，一年后可以以球员健康理由提前终止交易或根据球员的出场和表现以创俱乐部纪录的1250万美元（770万英镑）的身价买断球员。<ref name=BluesbagBenitez>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/page/News/NewsDetail/0,,10412~1715657,00.html |title=Blues bag Benitez |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=July 7, 2009 |accessdate=July 8, 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090710015635/http://www.bcfc.com/page/News/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10412~1715657%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-07-10 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.net/birmingham-sport/birmingham-city-fc/birmingham-city-fc-news/2009/07/08/birmingham-city-insist-on-get-out-clause-in-new-deal-for-christian-benitez-97319-24102744/ |work=Birmingham Mail |first=Colin |last=Tattum |date=July 8, 2009 |accessdate=August 19, 2009 |title=Birmingham City insist on 'get out' clause in new deal for Christian Benitez |quote=Blues will pay just $2 million, about £1.2 million, for the next 12 months and at the end of that period have a 'get out' option to cover themselves should Benitez's knee have caused him grief in that time. Thereafter, they will shell out money over a period of years, incorporating chunks for appearances and success, that could take the eventual price to $12.5 million, or £7.75 million. |archive-date=2012-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120328135759/http://www.birminghammail.net/birmingham-sport/birmingham-city-fc/birmingham-city-fc-news/2009/07/08/birmingham-city-insist-on-get-out-clause-in-new-deal-for-christian-benitez-97319-24102744/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>7月7日，贝尼特斯终于和伯明翰城签约，<ref name=BluesbagBenitez/>伯明翰城指出球员的加盟实际上是租借。<ref name=BCFCprofile>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10412~47565,00.html |title=Player Profiles: Christian Benitez |publisher=Birmingham City F.C |accessdate=May 7, 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090713044006/http://www.bcfc.com/page/ProfilesDetail/0%2C%2C10412~47565%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-07-13 }}</ref>在没有得到俱乐部允许的情况下，还在肩伤手术恢复期、等待英国签证的贝尼特斯擅自参加厄瓜多尔明星足球赛。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.net/birmingham-sport/birmingham-city-fc/birmingham-city-fc-news/2009/07/29/injury-hit-christian-benitez-plays-all-star-game-in-ecuador-97319-24266103/ |title=Injury-hit Christian Benitez plays all-star game in Ecuador |work=Birmingham Mail |first=Colin |last=Tattum |date=July 20, 2009 |accessdate=August 6, 2009 |archive-date=2012-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120328140933/http://www.birminghammail.net/birmingham-sport/birmingham-city-fc/birmingham-city-fc-news/2009/07/29/injury-hit-christian-benitez-plays-all-star-game-in-ecuador-97319-24266103/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2009年8月16日，贝尼特斯在伯明翰城客场0比1不敌[[曼彻斯特联足球俱乐部|曼联]]的比赛下半场替补出场，上演英超联赛首秀。他在比赛中险些追平比分，但被曼联门将[[賓·科士打_(足球運動員)|-{zh-hans:本·福斯特;zh-hk:賓·科士打;zh-tw:本·福斯特;}-]]“精彩的单手侧扑”化解。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8197957.stm |title=Man Utd 1–0 Birmingham |first=Pranav |last=Sonaji |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=August 16, 2009 |accessdate=August 16, 2009 |archive-date=2017-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806030531/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8197957.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>9月19日，贝尼特斯在伯明翰城对阵[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|赫尔城]]的比赛中首次首发登场，他表现出色，帮助球队1比0击败对手，媒体形容他“本来可以上演[[帽子戏法|帽子戏法]]，但却被对手门将[[博阿兹·米希尔|博阿兹·米希尔]]的神奇表现所化解”。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/article6841683.ece |title=Alex McLeish is full of hope for Christian Benítez at Birmingham |first=Jeremy |last=Cross |newspaper=[[The_Times|The Times]] |date=September 21, 2009 |accessdate=September 25, 2009}}</ref>11月9日，贝尼特斯射进他加盟伯明翰城的首个进球，帮助球队2比2逼平[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/article6910071.ece |title=Steven Gerrard's penalty rescues point for Liverpool |first=Oliver |last=Kay |newspaper=[[The_Times|The Times]] |date=November 10, 2009 |accessdate=November 10, 2009 |archive-date=2010-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100531035030/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/article6910071.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>贝尼特斯在2009/10赛季仅取得4个正式比赛进球，伯明翰城在赛季结束后试图重新谈判商定转会金额，但没有成功。伯明翰城决定不使用继续购买球员的条款，贝尼特斯回到桑托斯拉古纳。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.net/birmingham-sport/birmingham-city-fc/birmingham-city-fc-news/2010/05/14/birmingham-city-reasons-for-blues-not-signing-christian-benitez-explained-97319-26442822/ |title=Reasons for Blues not signing Christian Benitez explained |first=Colin |last=Tattum |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=May 14, 2010 |accessdate=May 14, 2010 |archive-date=2012-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120925092743/http://www.birminghammail.net/birmingham-sport/birmingham-city-fc/birmingham-city-fc-news/2010/05/14/birmingham-city-reasons-for-blues-not-signing-christian-benitez-explained-97319-26442822/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/8656185.stm|title=Birmingham City opt against signing Christian Benitez|date=May 14, 2010|work=BBC Sport|publisher=BBC|accessdate=May 18, 2010|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306060733/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/8656185.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===回归桑托斯拉古纳===
2010年7月21日，贝尼特斯回到桑托斯拉古纳并和球队签约3年合同。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Transfer-news-West-Ham-and-Sunderland-target-and-former-Birmingham-loanee-Christian-Benitez-signs-new-deal-in-Mexico-article532877.html|title=Former Birmingham loanee Benitez signs new deal in Mexico|date=July 21, 2010|work=Mirrror Football|accessdate=July 21, 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029204902/http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Transfer-news-West-Ham-and-Sunderland-target-and-former-Birmingham-loanee-Christian-Benitez-signs-new-deal-in-Mexico-article532877.html|archive-date=2013-10-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在回归的球队的第一个赛季（2010/11赛季春季联赛），他射进16球，成为联赛最佳射手，并率领球队进入春季联赛总决赛，但最终不敌[[蒙特雷足球俱乐部|蒙特雷]]屈居亚军。

===美洲===
[[File:Christian_Benitez_America.jpg|200px]]。]]
2011年5月22日，贝尼特斯转会加盟另一支墨西哥球队[[阿美利加足球俱樂部|美洲]]，据报道他的转会费高达1000万美元，创下墨西哥联赛转会的新纪录。7月24日，他在美洲2比1击败[[Querétaro_F.C.|克雷塔罗]]的比赛中射进加盟球队的首个进球。2011/12赛季秋季联赛，他射进14球，和[[Iván_Alonso|伊万·阿隆索]]并列射手榜首位。2012/13赛季春季联赛，贝尼特斯以11个进球和[[Esteban_Paredes|埃斯特班·帕雷德斯]]分享联赛最佳射手的称号。2012/13赛季秋季联赛，他射进17球，连续第三个赛季位列联赛射手榜首位。2013年5月26日，他在秋季联赛总决赛点球决战中射进第二个点球，帮助球队4比2击败[[蓝十字足球俱乐部|蓝十字]]获得冠军。

===阿尔贾什===
2013年7月6日，贝尼特斯以1170万欧元的身价加盟[[卡塔尔星级足球联赛|卡塔尔星级足球联赛]]球队[[艾查殊体育俱乐部|阿尔贾什]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cdn.alkass.net/news_details.aspx?news_id=55923|title=كما انفردنا ..الجيش يتعاقد رسميا مع الإكوادوري بينتيز|language=ar|date=6 July 2013|accessdate=6 July 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130708222912/http://cdn.alkass.net/news_details.aspx?news_id=55923|archive-date=2013-07-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>7月28日，他在[[Qatar_Sheikh_Jassem_Cup|谢赫贾西姆杯]]阿尔贾什对阵[[Qatar_SC|卡塔尔体育]]的比赛中首次代表球队在正式比赛出场，当时并未发现任何健康问题。<ref name=eljaish>{{cite web|url=http://dohanews.co/post/56787803061/qatar-footballer-dies-at-age-27-of-respiratory-arrest|title=Qatar footballer dies at age 27 of ‘respiratory arrest’|publisher=dohanews.co|date=July 29, 2013|accessdate=July 29, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130805191552/http://dohanews.co/post/56787803061/qatar-footballer-dies-at-age-27-of-respiratory-arrest|archive-date=2013-08-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>这也是他代表阿尔贾什参加的唯一一场比赛，一天后他死于[[心脏停搏|心脏停搏]]。

==国家队生涯==
[[File:Benitez.jpg|180px]]出场。]]
2005年，贝尼特斯首次入选[[厄瓜多尔国家足球队|厄瓜多尔国家足球队]]。他是厄瓜多尔参加[[2006年世界杯足球赛|2006年世界杯足球赛]]的成员，仅在小组赛厄瓜多尔0比3不敌[[德国国家足球队|德国]]的比赛中替补[[Felix_Borja|费利克斯·博尔哈]]出场。2006年9月6日，他在厄瓜多尔1比1战平[[秘鲁国家足球队|秘鲁]]的国际友谊赛中射进在国家队的首个进球。贝尼特斯在[[2007年美洲盃|2007年美洲盃]]厄瓜多尔参加的三场小组赛全部首发登场，并在和[[智利国家足球队|智利]]的比赛射进一球，但厄瓜多尔三战皆负被淘汰出局。他还参加了[[2011年美洲盃|2011年美洲盃]]，但没有进球。在[[2014年世界盃外圍賽_(南美洲區)|2010年世界盃外圍賽]]，他也有4球进账，帮助厄瓜多尔分别击败了[[委内瑞拉国家足球队|委内瑞拉]]、秘鲁、[[哥伦比亚国家足球队|哥伦比亚]]和[[巴拉圭国家足球队|巴拉圭]]，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/preliminaries/southamerica/matches/round=258419/match=300170246/index.html |title=Ecuador 2–0 Venezuela |accessdate=2013-07-30 |archive-date=2014-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140910123951/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/preliminaries/southamerica/matches/round=258419/match=300170246/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/preliminaries/southamerica/matches/round=258419/match=300170245/index.html |title=Ecuador 2–0 Peru |accessdate=2013-07-30 |archive-date=2014-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140813004124/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/preliminaries/southamerica/matches/round=258419/match=300170245/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/preliminaries/southamerica/matches/round=258419/match=300170268/index.html |title=Ecuador 1–0 Colombia |accessdate=2013-07-30 |archive-date=2014-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140910113022/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/preliminaries/southamerica/matches/round=258419/match=300170268/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/preliminaries/southamerica/matches/round=258419/match=300180909/index.html |title=Ecuador 4–1 Paraguay |accessdate=2013-07-30 |archive-date=2014-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140910120207/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/preliminaries/southamerica/matches/round=258419/match=300180909/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>这四场胜利也使得厄瓜多尔以6胜3平3负的成绩暂列南美洲区第三名。

==逝世==
2013年7月29日，贝尼特斯因强烈腹痛而进入[[卡塔尔|卡塔尔]][[多哈|多哈]]当地的一家医院。根据《马图蒂诺快报》的采访，他并未立即接受治疗并在几个小时后出现[[呼吸衰竭|呼吸衰竭]]。<ref>{{cite episode |title=Paralelo 23 |accessdate=July 29, 2013 |series=Paralelo 23 |credits=Ordorica, Ana Paula |network=[[Televisa|Televisa]] |station=FOROtv |city=[[Mexico_City|Mexico City]] |airdate=July 29, 2013 |began=11:30 |ended=13:00 ([[Central_Time_Zone|CST]]) |language=es}}</ref>最终他死于[[心脏停搏|心脏停搏]]的并发症，得年27岁。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23492978 |title=Christian Benitez: Former Birmingham striker dies aged 27 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=July 29, 2013 |accessdate=July 29, 2013 |archive-date=2015-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150421093246/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23492978 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.elcomercio.com/deportes/Chucho-Benitez-fallecio-Qatar-deceso-muerte_0_964703652.html |title=Christian Benítez falleció en Qatar |newspaper=El Comercio |language=es |date=July 29, 2013 |accessdate=July 29, 2013 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029222532/http://www.elcomercio.com/deportes/Chucho-Benitez-fallecio-Qatar-deceso-muerte_0_964703652.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

